Abstract rule action obr implementation. TODO: the best name of this class would be "ObrRuleActionImpl" instead of "ObrAbstractRuleActionImpl". The previous check in change the old "ObrRuleActionImpl" to "ObrModifyActionImpl". There will be an ADE issue if I still use "ObrRuleActionImpl" now. Will change the name during our FWM moving phase.
